description:
Woke up at sunrise, hair a mess, and not a care in the world. The light rays flowing elegantly through the glass. Setting my phone down in self timer to shutter the first moment. All the times I've spent on other photos with:

Lighting
Applying fake eyelashes
Tanning
Acrylic nails
Straightening hair
Filtering

So why is this one of my favorite photos? 0

7/24 6:52am
